            <title>[SOCIALLI-14] People search URI malformed causes LinkedIn to response with 400 Bad Request Error</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SOCIALLI-14</link>
                <project id="10608" key="SOCIALLI">Spring Social LinkedIn</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;URI for HTTP GET request for people search on LinkedIn REST API is badly formed.&lt;br/&gt;
It adds a &amp;amp; sign before keywords field and adds one extra &amp;amp; sign after the values that causes the 400 Bad Request Error response from LinkedIn &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Windows 7 Ultimate 64 bit, Java 32 bit</environment>
        <key id="41461">SOCIALLI-14</key>
            <summary>People search URI malformed causes LinkedIn to response with 400 Bad Request Error</summary>
